% k8s, helm

### Releases
# List failed releases
helm list --failed

# List all releases, even unhealthy ones
helm list -a

# List release history
helm history RELEASE

# List Kubernetes resources generated by a release revision
helm get manifest RELEASE --revision REVISION

# Force Helm release rollback(more likely to replace unhealthy resources)
helm rollback RELEASE REVISION --force

### Resources
# Helm Cheat Sheet
open https://helm.sh/docs/intro/cheatsheet/
